36(11)60648-X">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22185868/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Myocarditis&amp;author=S+Sagar&amp;author=PP+Liu&amp;author=LT+Cooper&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=Lancet&amp;pages=738-747&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0140-6736%2811%2960648-X&amp;pmid=22185868">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">4.</div><div id="r4" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Magnani JW, Dec GW. Myocarditis: current trends in diagnosis and treatment. <em>Circulation</em> 2006;113(6):876–890.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.105.584532">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16476862/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Myocarditis%3A+current+trends+in+diagnosis+and+treatment&amp;author=JW+Magnani&amp;author=GW+Dec&amp;publication_year=2006&amp;journal=Circulation&amp;pages=876-890&amp;doi=10.1161%2FCIRCULATIONAHA.105.584532&amp;pmid=16476862">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Troughton RW, Asher CR, Klein AL. Pericarditis. <em>Lancet</em> 2004;363(9410):717–727.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0140-6736(04)15648-1">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15001332/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Pericarditis&amp;author=RW+Troughton&amp;author=CR+Asher&amp;author=AL+Klein